{"article_id":"hVhaNVUTyB8bdh3k","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"This week 's Baltimore riot could not have happened to a nicer city .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Baltimore residents welcome strangers","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and even call them `` hon . ''","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"They sit on benches","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"painted with the slogan `` The Greatest City in America . ''","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Baltimore is also where people looted stores","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"and burned cars Monday night .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"They did it","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"when a man died","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"a week after being arrested .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"I was about to call Freddie Gray 's death the latest in a string of high-profile deaths of African-American men","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"involving police .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"But that 's not quite right .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"And that 's the point .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"Each incident of the past year was a particular story in a particular place ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"which became clear","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"as soon as we arrived in the very particular place","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that is Baltimore .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Nothing about this story was quite the way","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"it seemed from a distance .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"For one thing , the uprising did not bring a black populace into confrontation with an overwhelmingly white police force ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"as happened in Ferguson , Mo. , last year .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Baltimore , a majority black city , has a black mayor and a black police commissioner","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"whose force is about half black .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"This reality was plain to Taiwan Parker ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who lives in the neighborhood","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"where Gray was arrested .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"He told us","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"that police-community relations have long been sour .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"And yet ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"`` It ai n't no race thing -","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"it 's not a race thing at all . ''","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"His friend Michael Johnson agreed .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"In fact , much of West Baltimore seemed to agree .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"We interviewed 16 residents","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"- men and women , white and black , young and old .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Hardly anybody spoke of Freddie Gray 's death as a racial incident .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Parker views the trouble with police as an issue of class .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"In this neighborhood","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"where Freddie Gray was arrested ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"rundown , brick row-houses line the streets .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"A lot of drugs are sold - a lot .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"`` I 'm a three-time felon , ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"one man volunteered within minutes","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"of meeting us .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Parker says","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"he has a regular city job ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"but he feels","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"some cops view everyone as a criminal .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"`` Some of them , they label us , ''","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"`` They see us down here ,","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"they label us as drug dealers ,","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"we live in poverty .","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"That 's not all true . ''","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"On the morning after Monday 's violence , residents of this area were busy on almost every street","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"- bagging up debris from a looted liquor store","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"or pushing brooms along the sidewalk .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"They did this","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"even though they were n't sure","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"the violence was over .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"A helicopter hung overhead , motionless ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"as if suspended from a string .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Waiting for something to happen .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"Volunteers delivered sack lunches to children .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"The kids had lost their free lunches","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"when the schools closed due to violence .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"There was also food for grownups .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"In a more prosperous neighborhood , Bob McCulley offered a plate of jalapeno corn muffins and more .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"That 's Baltimore :","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the place","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"you get offered a wide selection of snacks in a riot zone .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"McCulley is a retired cop .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"We met him in front of a strip mall .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"The shops included his wife 's looted hardware store .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"he and his wife arrived at the damaged store on Monday night","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"to find neighbors","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"waiting for them to help clean up the mess .","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"They were friendly neighbors -","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"who worked alongside friendly looters at the shop next door .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"`` The neighbors boarded up the front of the hardware store","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"as the people were still looting the Rite Aid , ''","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"McCulley said .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"`` And they 're pulling up in cars","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"and they 're taking stuff from the front of Rite Aid","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and they 're taking stuff from the back of Rite Aid . ''","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"Many people in this city had been hoping for a less-violent outcome .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"One of them was Lillian Hoover , a teacher","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"we met outside the hardware store .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"She remembered a protest last Saturday ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"before violence erupted .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"`` If you look at the pictures , ''","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"she said ,","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"`` you can see","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"it 's a mixed crowd of people , different ages ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"there 's people with strollers .","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"You know ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"it 's really a diverse crowd .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"And I was so hopeful .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"You know ,","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"I was thinking :","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"'This is Baltimore .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Baltimore is going to show the country how to do this . ' ``","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Then Monday 's violence came ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"and `` The Greatest City in America '' did n't seem as great .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"At a park some blocks away , we met Farrah Spruill .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"She was sitting on bleachers with her 6-year-old son .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"I asked","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"what she thought","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"about raising a boy in Baltimore right now .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"`` That 's a loaded question , ''","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"`` I 'm scared for my child every day . ''","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"But she was doing what she could .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"She 'd come to the park for a community meeting .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"More than 100 people gathered at one end of the basketball courts .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Activists urged parents to bring their kids to this park","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"while the schools were closed :","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"They could play basketball ,","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"get some adult supervision","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"and stay out of trouble .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"`` We know the real Baltimore , ''","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"one called out to the crowd .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"And he asked for help","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"regaining what their city had lost .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":136,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":131,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":0,"right":130,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":128,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":132,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":7,"right":133,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":181,"right":251,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":181,"left":139,"right":180,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":139,"left":138,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":137,"right":12,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":144,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":142,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":14,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":15,"right":